---
title: Italian Chicken Mini-Meatball Soup with White Beans, Parmesan & Buttered Baguette
description: For this riff on Italian wedding soup, mini sausage meatballs steal the show. They simmer in a garlicky tomato broth with beans, carrots, and scallions until tender. Sprinkle your bowls with umami-rich Parmesan cheese and serve with buttery toasted baguette for a hearty, comforting meal in just 20 minutes.
